---
title: Hawaiian-Inspired Chicken Tacos with Charred Pineapple and Roasted Red Pepper Salsa
description: Succulent chicken is glazed in a sweet and sticky sauce, with creamy coleslaw and zingy roasted red pepper and pineapple salsa in these Hawaiian-inspired tacos. Transport your tastebuds to the tropics!

